{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881350/extras/OM_Header_Banner_GIF.gif?t=1698691033\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881350/extras/OM_Banner_InspiredByHistory.png?t=1698691033\" /><br><br>The Odyssey of the Mammoth takes you back to the Stone Age 12,000 years ago. Play as a mammoth mother and guide your calf to Wrangel Island, the last known haven of mammothkind.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881350/extras/OM_Banner_EpicBattles.png?t=1698691033\" /><br><br>Show your might and take part in fights of pachydermian proportions! Lead your calf during combat, charge through the crowd, and stomp your enemies.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881350/extras/OM_Banner_BreathtakingSights.png?t=1698691033\" /><br><br>Between battles, enjoy an amazing view. Discover three colorful environments: the vast steppes, the lush taiga and the arctic glaciers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881350/extras/OM_Banner_EndearingTale.png?t=1698691033\" /><br><br>Experience the mammoths\u2019 extinction through the voice of an involved narrator, as he leads you on your journey giving you advices, facts about the era, and even some sarcastic puns.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881350/extras/OM_Banner_Features.png?t=1698691033\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Three beautiful environments to discover from a third person perspective<br></li><li>Three different attacks to deal with predators: tusk sweep, charge and stomp<br></li><li>A dynamic narrator<br></li><li>A complete saving system including checkpoints and 3 saving slots<br></li><li>An original soundtr